Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:00.53,0:00:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:14.58,0:00:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,天空好藍 你露出了微笑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.32,0:00:28.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不經意的一句話使內心相繫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.32,0:00:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,穿上鞋子敞開門扉的後方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:37.07,0:00:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你重合的景色使我心動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:46.98,0:00:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花綻放之未來戀夢\N加速的心跳無法壓抑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.95,0:01:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人共同感受  季節不斷更替
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.49,0:01:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無可取代的瞬間\N編織著邂逅的物語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.47,0:01:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對紛飛的櫻花許下心願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.51,0:01:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,向前行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:21.41,0:01:23.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,花盛開著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.75,0:01:37.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第九話  神祕詩人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:43.20,0:01:43.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.77,0:01:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我滿懷我內心的愛意\N為妳送上一百朵玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.74,0:01:52.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一半代表我們認識之前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:52.34,0:01:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一半代表我們認識之後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.04,0:01:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從此我將成為妳的玫瑰陪伴妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.28,0:02:01.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:02.02,0:02:04.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時散發出甜美香味令妳陶醉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.62,0:02:10.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時以愛的荊棘刺痛妳的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:11.23,0:02:15.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時又宛如花瓣溫柔地擁抱妳
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.06,0:02:16.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,-有時則是…\N-哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.50,0:02:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,玩笑開過頭可是會短命的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.51,0:02:26.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以別再惡搞了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:28.34,0:02:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,竟然浪費這份難得的禮物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:31.41,0:02:35.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是今早跟這首詩一起寄來的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:36.72,0:02:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你擅自看過了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:38.59,0:02:40.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為沒封起來就看了，對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:40.86,0:02:42.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是羞死人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.46,0:02:46.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是啊\N竟然寫得出這麼肉麻的詩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.73,0:02:49.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才不是啦\N竟然這麼大聲的唸出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.63,0:02:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥不能幫我著想一點嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:52.00,0:02:52.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,著想？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.07,0:02:54.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼，可以吃嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:55.04,0:02:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還想要被處罰嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:57.24,0:02:58.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我錯了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.37,0:03:02.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過真奇怪，居然沒有署名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.11,0:03:06.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概是認為就算沒有署名\N音夢心裡也會有個底吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.12,0:03:08.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我才不知道呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.82,0:03:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得有拿過這種東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.89,0:03:12.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別這麼斷言啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:12.49,0:03:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽起來可是頗悲哀的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.02,0:03:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.93,0:03:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是會是誰呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:18.59,0:03:22.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以確定的是\N這傢伙根本沒有想像力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.70,0:03:25.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在櫻花永不凋謝的島上送玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.77,0:03:28.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就好像吃蛋糕吃到飽之後\N還追加一份紅豆冰對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.27,0:03:33.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道是在吃醋嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.04,0:03:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有些微妙呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.64,0:03:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,身為一個哥哥\N當然會在意妹妹的感情狀況
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.08,0:03:42.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.65,0:03:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.49,0:03:48.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.12,0:03:49.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:50.76,0:03:53.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,感覺好像有人在看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.03,0:03:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許是那位神祕詩人喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.20,0:03:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.17,0:04:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，這個是…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.71,0:04:08.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花是櫻花，玫瑰是玫瑰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.68,0:04:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕和紅豆冰也是不同類
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.51,0:04:13.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的心為妳而碎\N（三句日文句尾音同）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:14.65,0:04:16.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個人頭殼壞掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.79,0:04:18.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.55,0:04:22.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙剛剛偷聽我們的談話吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.23,0:04:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是那個傢伙嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.00,0:04:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:28.06,0:04:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想怎樣啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.86,0:04:33.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就像狗尾草挑弄你的心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.80,0:04:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別用吟詩的方式回答我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.24,0:04:36.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,友情變成憎恨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.01,0:04:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,男人與男人拳頭相向
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.81,0:04:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這雖然是我所夢想的場景
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.14,0:04:44.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但很遺憾那個人不是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.38,0:04:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那你就早點說啊，真是愛搗蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.95,0:04:50.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跨出這一步他就變成熟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.02,0:04:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,內心吹起了一陣微風
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.59,0:04:55.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.76,0:04:57.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼不是你嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.60,0:05:02.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.23,0:05:06.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.47,0:05:11.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來這個詩人是跟蹤狂\N還是朝倉妹妹的信徒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.41,0:05:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然能自由進出教室\N那就是這裡的學生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.04,0:05:18.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說在前，可不是我啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:18.25,0:05:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛朝倉才盤問過我呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.92,0:05:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那會是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.42,0:05:24.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢，妳心裡有底嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.63,0:05:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.30,0:05:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:35.86,0:05:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,朝倉音夢，在為感情煩惱嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.87,0:05:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.14,0:05:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.30,0:05:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老師
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:44.44,0:05:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事，朝倉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.94,0:05:50.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她從早上就有點發燒\N我本來要她請假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.14,0:05:52.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以讓她去保健室休息一下嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:53.65,0:05:56.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看在哥哥這麼溫柔我就准吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.32,0:05:57.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.82,0:05:58.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們走吧，音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.46,0:06:02.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我先告辭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.83,0:06:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，謝謝你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.67,0:06:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算要妳別太在意\N也不太可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:13.80,0:06:14.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過別在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.11,0:06:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的要睡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.31,0:06:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是這麼跟曆老師說的\N所以沒辦法啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.48,0:06:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真糟糕，沒半個人在嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.35,0:06:33.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不要一個人啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.99,0:06:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥留在這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.76,0:06:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去的話不太好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.86,0:06:40.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等等不知道會被杉並說些什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.06,0:06:42.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:43.87,0:06:46.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，就算你會煩也求求你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.71,0:06:54.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一般這樣哪睡得著啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.09,0:07:04.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:05.52,0:07:07.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,過來這裡，歌丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:09.16,0:07:11.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了歌丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.16,0:07:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從現在起你就是音夢的保鑣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.90,0:07:16.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽懂了嗎，保鑣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:18.17,0:07:21.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不在的時候由你來保護音夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.30,0:07:21.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,知道了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:24.17,0:07:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底聽懂沒啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.91,0:07:33.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我就相信你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.48,0:07:36.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌丸，歌丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.98,0:07:38.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底跑哪兒去了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.12,0:07:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,涮涮鍋～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了嗎，真子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.90,0:07:55.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在想音夢的事情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:56.14,0:08:00.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候應該邀請她\N一起吃火鍋比較好吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:01.01,0:08:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說的也是，下次我會邀她的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.45,0:08:07.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那真子也來涮一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.22,0:08:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥…？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.46,0:08:23.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等一下，別生氣啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.10,0:08:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正比起妹妹的安全\N哥哥更在意外界的眼光
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.60,0:08:31.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼叫外界的眼光啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.24,0:08:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比如說跟妹妹傳出緋聞之類的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.18,0:08:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.65,0:08:39.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這當然會困擾吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.18,0:08:40.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道妳不會困擾嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:41.02,0:08:43.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且妳這樣對歌丸太失禮了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.78,0:08:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,牠答應過我會好好保護妳的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:48.36,0:08:49.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.56,0:08:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,反正就是要自己保護自己對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.69,0:08:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以我都說歌丸牠…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.30,0:09:03.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥那個笨蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.88,0:09:13.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.02,0:09:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你想幹什麼啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.52,0:09:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我只是在想\N能不能從這裡爬到屋頂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.86,0:10:00.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別查了啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:00.60,0:10:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種時候\N一定要清查閣樓和地下室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.90,0:10:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥，你好像很開心耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.01,0:10:13.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳也是啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.78,0:10:19.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有點像小時候在玩祕密基地呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.55,0:10:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有異常
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.02,0:10:25.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起碼知道神祕詩人\N沒有躲在閣樓裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,回去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.52,0:10:28.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼回去呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:28.26,0:10:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,換個方向不就得了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.69,0:10:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:33.06,0:10:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為如果我先走的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:36.06,0:10:37.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我穿裙子…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:37.80,0:10:38.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.07,0:10:40.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那我先走就行了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.08,0:10:48.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請進
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.82,0:11:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我睡不著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:03.42,0:11:07.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在保健室睡得那麼熟\N無論是誰都會失眠吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:08.46,0:11:09.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,進來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥講故事給妳聽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:20.47,0:11:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌丸，會感冒喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.38,0:11:29.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歌丸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.35,0:11:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可疑的傢伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.75,0:11:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,等這根蠟燭的火燄熄滅時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.02,0:11:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳的生命之火也將熄滅
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當老婆婆說完這些話後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:42.10,0:11:45.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,便將滿嘴的口臭味\N向蠟燭的火燄吹去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:45.87,0:11:46.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.74,0:11:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳有聽到什麼嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.41,0:11:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有小偷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:54.34,0:11:56.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別跑～別跑～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.11,0:12:00.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:01.05,0:12:02.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我站住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.80,0:12:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:19.73,0:12:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小櫻，到底怎麼了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.77,0:12:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我看到可疑人物\N想潛入音夢的房間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:26.27,0:12:27.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是被他逃掉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.75,0:12:41.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,月光所映照的白皙肌膚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.42,0:12:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由飄散於空氣中\N微薄的櫻花香味所包圍
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.16,0:12:51.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小夢和我的邂逅\N將永遠刻在我的記憶裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.84,0:12:57.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好想見妳啊，小夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.71,0:12:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小夢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:59.31,0:13:00.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你到底是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:06.31,0:13:07.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:07.45,0:13:10.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你問小夢或許比較快吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:11.29,0:13:12.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他是誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.45,0:13:13.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我怎麼可能認識啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.09,0:13:15.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.32,0:13:18.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是小夢說想見我\N我才為妳而來的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.36,0:13:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小夢…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.06,0:13:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在胡說什麼\N我完全不認識你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.10,0:13:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妳是說真的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:30.00,0:13:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是說真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.97,0:13:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要說得這麼欺負人呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.24,0:13:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對於小夢我可是瞭如指掌啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.85,0:13:42.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像是妳背後這裡有一顆小痣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.35,0:13:45.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雙腳的食指比拇指長
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.65,0:13:49.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還有睡覺時是穿什麼樣的睡衣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.09,0:13:51.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.33,0:13:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對了，當妳收到這首詩時\N應該很高興吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:55.46,0:13:58.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要化為櫻花花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.77,0:14:03.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飄落在妳的頭髮\N手心及嘴唇上輕輕撫摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.24,0:14:04.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你為什麼會知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.77,0:14:07.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花因為會瞬間凋謝才美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.14,0:14:10.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許有人會這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.48,0:14:13.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我喜歡這座島上的櫻花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.11,0:14:16.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為會永遠在妳的身邊綻放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.38,0:14:18.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,別再說了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.69,0:14:21.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我寄給小薰的詩\N你會知道內容呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:23.79,0:14:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你難道是小薰？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:27.43,0:14:31.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯，不過應該叫我薰就行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.70,0:14:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個小薰不是女孩子嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.04,0:14:36.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼這樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.17,0:14:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小夢一直把我當成是女生嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.67,0:14:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不～～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.28,0:14:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼妳那些扣人心弦的詩\N以及溫柔的話語
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.14,0:14:47.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全部是以為我是女生才寫的嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:47.28,0:14:48.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:48.38,0:14:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的天啊～
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.92,0:14:51.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛，這傢伙吵死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.59,0:14:54.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實在太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.92,0:14:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到小夢有這樣的嗜好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.59,0:15:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是啦，等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:01.30,0:15:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來是這麼一回事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不對，不是那樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.53,0:15:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我和薰是在詩歌討論區認識的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:08.44,0:15:10.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我一直以為他是女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.60,0:15:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:11.57,0:15:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不，我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:12.97,0:15:14.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想不到音夢居然這麼糊塗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.95,0:15:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢，那些詩原本要寫給誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.98,0:15:24.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也沒有要給誰啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.49,0:15:27.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎，那我可以拿來用嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.96,0:15:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想要化為櫻花花瓣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.83,0:15:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,飄落在你的頭髮\N手心及嘴唇上輕輕撫摸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.56,0:15:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花因為會瞬間凋謝才美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.60,0:15:41.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許有人會這麼說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過我喜歡這座島上的櫻花
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.24,0:15:49.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為會永遠在你的身邊綻放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.89,0:16:08.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥，只有今晚就好\N我可以跟你一起睡嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.60,0:16:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就像小時候那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟發生很多事情呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.90,0:16:16.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有今晚而已喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.15,0:16:31.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,預告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:31.19,0:16:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到小薰居然是個男生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.79,0:16:35.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是嚇我一大跳呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.92,0:16:37.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢，妳這樣實在太過份了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.99,0:16:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,薰你還在啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:40.16,0:16:41.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我當然還在
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.26,0:16:42.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過小夢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.30,0:16:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果妳願意的話，我不介意\N妳把我當成女生來愛我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.80,0:16:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,網路上看不到對方的臉\N實在有點恐怖呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.77,0:16:52.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是能看清對方的內心\N也是蠻麻煩的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.27,0:16:54.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,下次是園遊會的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:54.41,0:16:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,白河同學要在發表會唱歌呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:56.91,0:16:58.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,她還要參加選美嗎？\N（第十話 希望你聆聽）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.02,0:17:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蒐集心的碎片  想趕快送給你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.70,0:17:21.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎快要滿溢  真是不可思議
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.37,0:17:31.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,兩人漫步於鈴音輕響的樹蔭下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.05,0:17:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合而為一的影子\N高興地凝視著夕陽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.42,0:17:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,櫻花之雨紛飛著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.16,0:17:50.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,由樹梢陽光所籠罩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.93,0:17:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在累積於胸口的哀傷啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.24,0:18:06.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,更替的季節與不變的笑容
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:06.51,0:18:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定會演奏通往未來的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:14.76,0:18:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,閉上眼睛總是能見到你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.66,0:18:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟你在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:38.05,0:18:39.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早啊哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.38,0:18:45.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,醒來了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.86,0:18:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真是愛賴床呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.64,0:19:05.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再不快起來就要遲到囉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.51,0:19:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有忘記帶什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒問題的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.62,0:19:17.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就走吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.27,0:19:36.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好久沒跟哥哥並肩走在一起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.87,0:20:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,差不多該回家囉，哥哥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.16,0:20:34.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你這個白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:47.64,0:20:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.18,0:20:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我吃飽了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.75,0:20:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.58,0:20:54.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.92,0:20:55.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.22,0:21:05.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢，要喝茶嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.89,0:21:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:37.76,0:21:38.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥你這個大白癡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:48.07,0:21:48.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:51.64,0:21:55.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,打開廁所或是浴室時\N要注意一下啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:04.99,0:22:05.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,該睡了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:08.59,0:22:10.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,晚安
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:12.79,0:22:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,音夢，回自己的房間睡啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.27,0:22:20.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是拿妳沒辦法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.39,0:23:18.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,討厭，別看啦
